CS 845 AH 414 CH 665 SDAH 439   
 ### 5: MUNZI ULI KULE SENA?   
HOW FAR FROM HOME?

Doh is Eb

  **1.**   
Munzi uli kule sena? Nda ka mu buzya mulindi,   
Wa ka amba: &#210;Masiku a yeya ku mana;   
Leka ku lila, fwambana;   
Cisyomyo ci la ku kweenzya   
Limwi u ka sike Ku &#212;nyika ya kusalala.&#211;

  **2.**   
Nda ka buzya syilumamba, Wa ka imba lwimbo olu;   
&#210;Ndalwanisya abukano, Ndila koma koonse;   
Utalili bikilila, Limwi mulimo wamana.   
Tuli zyi tu la ku pegwa colwe, no twa koma.&#211;

  **3.**   
Munzi wesu tuli kule, Kuyeya kubotu oku!   
Kulakomanisya mwenzu Mumusinzo wakwe;   
Utalili, tu la ku Swangana kutamani, kwakwe,   
Kupenga kwa mana tu li Mu munzi wa Tata

CS 26   
 ### 103 MUZYALWE ALIMWI   
YE MUST BE BORN AGAIN

Doh is Eb

  **1.**   
Muleli wakaya kuli Jesu,   
Kubuzya inzila ya lufutuko,   
Jesu wakasandulula kabotu   
Uzyalwe alimwi

  **CIINDULULO:**   
&#210;Uzyalwe alimwi,&#211; Uzyalwe alimwi   
Kasimpe ime ndakwambila kuti,   
&#210;Uzyalwe alimwi.&#211;

  **2.**   
Inywe amutelele makani,   
Nga&#213;kaambisya Jesu Mwami wesu;   
Makani aya atabi abuyo;   
&#210;Muzyalwe alimwi,&#211;

  **3.**   
Inywe no mu yanda kulyokezya,   
Akwiimba aba setekene bakwe;   
Mwayanda kufutuka kutamani;   
&#210;Muzyalwe alimwi.&#211;

CS 734 AH 409 CH 180   
 ### 154 MULINDI NDAAMBILE   
WATCHMAN TELL ME

Doh is G

  **1.**   
Mulindi ndizyibye zyoonse, Bulemu bwa Zioni;   
Zibonisyo zya ku boola, Sena zya libonyesya,   
Silweendo kolangisisya, Kumweka mu makumbi,   
Sama zikobelo zyako, Bwaca lino Nyamuka.

  **2.**   
Mulindi langa kumweka, Kusalazya Inzila;   
Zibonisyo zilaamba, Kubola kwa Muvuni,   
Impeta nozilalila, Kuzwa munyika &#212;lwizi;   
Basale bali muzyumbwe, Babuka tabakafwi.

  **3.**   
Mulindi bona kumweka, Kwa buzuba bwa Mwami;   
Mazwi ala kambauka, Bulelo bula &#212;afwafwi,   
Silwendo ndabona kunze, Milyango ya Kenani;   
Munzi wakwe wa Bulemu, Wali bonya mu julu.

  **4.**   
Mulindi we wa mumunzi, Acuno cisalala;   
Ulisamide bubotu, Muleli wa Zioni,   
Oko kwitala &#212;mulundu, kumweka kwali bonya;   
Kula libonya atala, A milonga a miinzo.

  **5.**   
Mulindi wabona nyika, Ya micelo maluba;   
Okuya kuli kuseka, Ku munzi wa Edeni,   
Komvwa nyimbo zilaimbwa, Zila mvwika muluwo;   
Komvwa banji mbobaimba, Nobanjila mumunzi.

CS 566 AH 352 SDAH  573   
 ### 155 NDAUNKA NKOYANDA   
I&#213;LL GO WHERE YOU WANT ME TO GO

Doh is F

  **1.**   
Nokutabi mu malundu na ba atala a lwizi;   
Nokutabi kulwana nkondo, Mwami ulandiita,   
Naakuti wandiita kuunka, koonse oko nkwetazyi;   
Ndiya kuvuna ku Mwami, &#210;Nditume konse nkoyanda ndiunke.&#211;

  **CIINDULULO:**   
Ndilaunka konse nkondituma, Mumalundu, a mulwizi;   
Ndila kanana zyoonse nzyondituma, Ndila kuba   
Mbondiyanda.

  **2.**   
Antela ndielede kwaamba majwi a Jesu, Ngayanda;   
Nakuba mubisyi mucibi ngwetikayandaule;   
Muvuni ba mugwasyi wangu, Nzila noisiya mbi;   
Ndila tola mulumbe mubotu, Ndilakanana ncoyanda.

  **3.**   
Kuli munzi mumuunda wakwe, Kutebula takuko;   
Oko nkwetibelekele lyoonse, A Jesu wakayaswa,   
Ndisyome mu luse lwa Jesu, A kuzyiba luyando,   
Ndila cita luyando lwako, Ndila kuba mbondiyanda.

CS 723 AH 203 CH 245 SDAH 533   
 ### 173 O LUSYOMO   
O FOR A FAITH

Doh is Bb

  **1.**   
O lusyomo lutasimpi nakuba masunko;   
O lutatyompwi nakuba mu bucete,   
Nakuba mu nkondo, Nakuba mu bucete.

  **2.**   
Olu luta tongauki nakuba mapenzi;   
Pele muku ciswa konse luya kujata;   
Ku Mwami Leza lula jata, kuli Leza.

  **3.**   
Lusyomo lumweka konse, Maiwe na uma;   
Mumasunko talu yoowi, Taku ku yoowa;   
Musinze onse, taaku ku yoowa.

  **4.**   
Lukoma masunko onse A Ku inda zyonse;   
Nakuba lwizi lwa zibi, Talu kakomi;   
Lusyomo lwini talu komwi lusyomo.

  **5.**   
Mwami ndipe lusyomo lwakuti ndikazunde   
Ndila kumvwa zileleko zya ku munzi utamani;   
Eezyo zya mu munzi utamani.

CS 878 AH 400 CH 540 SDAH 604   
 ### 180 TATUZI CIINDI   
WE KNOW NOT THE HOUR

  **1.**   
Tatuzyi ciindi ca kuboola kwa Mwami;   
A zibonisyo zitu tondezya zyonse kuboola kwakwe;   
Nce cisyomyo cibotu, Ta tu cizyi cindi.

  **CIINDULULO:**   
Ula ku &#201;&#201;..Bola, atulibambe,   
Ula ku &#201;&#201;..Bola, colwe, Aleluya,   
Ula ku &#201;&#201;..Bola, Mumakumbi asalala;   
Ta tu cizyi ciindi.

  **2.**   
Kusalala kwa bayanda kufutuka;   
Nkokali kasimpe mwi Bbuku lya Leza;   
Lila tutondezya kusimpila konse;   
Tatu cizyi ciindi.

  **3.**   
Tula kulinda akupaila &#212;nguwe;   
Tula nyona limwi aka boole,   
Tula kwiimba notu bona zibonisyo.   
Tatu cizyi ciindi.

Cs 652 Ch 398 Ah 297 Sdah 551   
 ### 202 JESU NDI SOLOLELE   
JESUS SAVIOUR PILOT ME

  **1.**   
Jesu ndi sololele, Mu masunko a nyika;   
Mapenzi naa vula, Ndiyube muli ndiwe;   
Ndijane munzi kwako, Jesu Ndi sololela.

  **2.**   
Mbuli mwana ulila, Kondipa kuumuna;   
Maiwe a mulwizi, A la kutelelesya,   
O Muleli wa lwizi, Jesu ndisololele.

  **3.**   
Nenda sika ku nkomwe, Maiwe naa ndenzya;   
Kondipa ku lyokezya, Ndicili muli ndiwe;   
A ndi kumvwe noita, &#210;Ndila kusololela.&#211;

Cs 193 AH 154 CH 526   
 ### 203 MUKOMANISYI WASIKA   
THE COMFORTER HAS COME

  **1.**   
Kotuma mulumbe, Konse kuli bantu,   
Ubazyibye bonse, Bantu ba mapenzi;   
Ba Klistu baimbe, Kukomana kwakwe;   
Siluse Wasika.

  **CIINDULULO:**   
Siluse wasika, Siluse wasika;   
Muya usalala wa Tata wa pegwa,   
Kotuma mulumbe, konse kuli bantu;   
Siluse wasika.

  **2.**   
Busiku bwa mana izuba lilazwa,   
Kulila kwamvwika a kunyema konse,   
Kwiinda mu malundu, Izuba lya bbila,   
Siluse wasika.

  **3.**   
O Mwami wa bami a nguzu ziponya;   
Ku babisyi bonse, Upa lufutuko;   
Mu myoyo ya bantu, Lwimbo lwa kukoma   
Siluse wasika.

  **4.**   
O luyando lwini, ndikaambe buti;   
Kuli basoweki, A luse lupati,   
Ndi mwana wa zibi, Ndi mweke anguwe;   
Siluse wasika.

  **5.**   
Atumvwike konse, Notu muimbila,   
Basale ku julu, Baimbe andiswe;   
Mu luyando lwakwe, Lwiimbo lwesu ndolu;   
Siluse wasika.

Cs 45 Ah 167 Ch 564   
 ### 205 JESU NACIPETEKEZYA   
WHILE JESUS WHISPERS

Doh is F

  **1.**   
Na cita Jesu kobola, We mubi;   
Notu ciku pailila, Kobola,   
Komutambula mu moyo, We mubi,   
Lino nce cindi cibotu, Kobola.

  **2.**   
Na wa lemenwa bunene, We mubi;   
Ula kuku vuna Jesu, Kobola;   
Jesu takwe kuku cenga, We mubi;   
Jesu ula kufutula, Kobola.

  **3.**   
O ula ku kombelezya, We mubi;   
Kobola aku leleke, Kobola;   
Jesu na ciita kobola, We mubi;   
Natu ciku pailila, Kobola.

CS 200   
 ### 223 CILILA KOONSE   
FOLLOW ALL THE WAY

Doh is G

  **1.**   
Ndila mumvwa Mufutuli, Ula ndiita mucilile;   
Mu moyo lilamba ijwi, Lila ita bola we mubi.

  **CIINDULULO:**   
Ndila kubweza Ciingano, Ndicilile Mufutuli;   
Nkwaya kundisololela, Kucilila munzila yonse.

  **2.**   
Kuti nzila ila &#212;mamvwa, Amaulu akatede;   
Moyo wangu �lakomana, Ndicilile munzila yonse.

  **3.**   
Mu cibanda konditola, Ndisanine kulya kwako;   
Ndikuyande ziindi zyonse, Ndicilile munzila yonse;

  **4.**   
Konditola a luboko,  A luyando lutamani;   
Undi kwel&#213;a luse lwako, Ndicilile munzila yonse.

### 321 JESU NE NZILA   
 JESUS IS THE WAY

  **1.**   
Jesu nenzila iya kuli taata;   
Iya kuli Taata, Iya kuli Taata,   
Jesu ne nzila iya kuli Taata;   
Kuli kukomana, Kukomana lyoonse.

  **2.**   
Koboola tweende ku nganda ya Taata;   
Kunganda ya Taata, kunganda ya Taata;   
Koboola tweende kunganda ya Taata,   
Kuli kukomana, kukomana lyoonse.

  **3.**   
Nkasame musyini munganda ya Taata;   
Munganda ya Taata, Munganda ya Taata;   
Nkasame musyini munganda ya Taata,   
Kuli kukomana, kukomana lyoonse.
